Finally
The application rendered user-controlled input directly inside a FreeMarker template without proper sanitization,
allowing template expressions to be evaluated.

Key Takeaways
Always identify the template engine before attempting further testing.
Official documentation is often enough to understand available template features.
Never render untrusted input as template code.
